__data__.text:
Emergency Helpline Numbers with Descriptions
NATIONAL EMERGENCY NUMBER
Number: 112
Description: A universal emergency number for all urgent situations.
POLICE
Number: 100 or 112
Description: Contact police in case of crime, violence, or any security threat.
FIRE
Number: 101
Description: Call the fire department in case of fire emergencies.
AMBULANCE
Number: 102
Description: Call for an ambulance during medical emergencies.
Disaster Management Services
Number: 108
Description: For immediate assistance during natural disasters and accidents.
Women Helpline
Number: 1091
Description: Support for women in distress, harassment, and safety concerns.
Women Helpline - ( Domestic Abuse )
Number: 181
Description: Helpline for victims of domestic violence seeking help and protection.
Air Ambulance
Number: 9540161344
Description: For emergency air ambulance services in critical medical conditions.
Aids Helpline
Number: 1097
Description: Information and support for HIV/AIDS-related queries.
Anti Poison ( New Delhi )
Number: 1066 or 011-1066
Description: For poisoning cases requiring immediate medical advice.
Disaster Management ( N.D.M.A )

Number: 1078, 011-26701700
Description: National Disaster Management Authority helpline for disaster-related assistance.
EARTHQUAKE / FLOOD / DISASTER ( N.D.R.F Headquarters )
Number: 011-24363260 , 9711077372
Description: NDRF helpline for natural disaster relief and rescue operations.
Railway Enquiry
Number: 139
Description: Check train schedules, delays, and railway services.
Senior Citizen Helpline
Number: 14567
Description: Support and assistance for senior citizens in distress.
Road Accident Emergency Service
Number: 1073
Description: Report road accidents and get emergency support.
Road Accident Emergency Service On National Highway For Private Operators
Number: 1033
Description: Emergency services for accidents on national highways.
Kisan Call Centre
Number: 18001801551
Description: Helpline for farmers to get agricultural guidance and support.
Relief Commissioner For Natural Calamities
Number: 1070
Description: For relief assistance during natural calamities and disasters.
Children In Difficult Situation
Number: 1098
Description: Child helpline for children in distress and abuse cases.
National Poisons Information Centre - AIIMS NEW DELHI ( 24*7 )
Number: 1800116117 , 011-26593677, 26589391
Description: For poisoning emergencies requiring expert advice.
Poison Information Centre ( CMC , Vellore )
Number: 18004251213
Description: CMC Vellores helpline for poison-related emergencies.
Tourist Helpline
Number: 1363 or 1800111363

Description: Helpline for tourists in India needing assistance.
LPG Leak Helpline
Number: 1906
Description: Emergency helpline for LPG gas leak incidents.
KIRAN MENTAL HEALTH Helpline
Number: 18005990019
Description: Mental health support for individuals experiencing stress or mental distress.
CYBER CRIME HELPLINE
Number: 1930
Description: Report cyber frauds, scams, and online crimes.
COVID 19 HELPLINE
Number: 011-23978046 OR 1075
Description: Helpline for COVID-19 related queries and emergencies.
